{"tid":1430682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【重要】 監控燈柱屄過送中","createTime":"2019-08-07T20:30:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T20:41:14.000Z","uid":299171,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6e6ce70c3a778301af746c5d68e867605b0d2a66","tid":1430682,"uid":299171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T20:30:51.000Z","msg":"現時五大訴求集中講反送中<br />\n但喺林奠同政虎尻縮嘅同時<br />\n唔少巴絲已經講過<br />\n同新疆監控牌子嘅監控鏡頭<br />\n已經喺各區開始出現<br />\n觀塘區更已經有監控燈柱<br />\n<br />\n一旦政虎作出施捨式嘅讓步<br />\n例如林奠辭職<br />\n成立偽獨立調查委員會之類<br />\n運動會步向瓦解<br />\n喺監控系統嘅存在同義士被清算下<br />\n之後再想出嚟對抗監控評分系統<br />\n會難上加難<br />\n<br />\n明明監控評分系統、監控燈柱<br />\n比送中屄十萬九千倍<br />\n點解無人煲大佢？<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求應加入第六第七項<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">拆除監控燈柱<br />\n永久擱置監控評分系統</span></span></strong><br />\n喺威脅未除嘅時候運動唔可以停止<br />\n<br />\n監控評分系統好撚大鑊<br />\n乜撚嘢衝紅燈買翻版扣分都係掩眼法<br />\n佢重點係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">批評政府扣分扣得金過造毒奶粉<br />\n「造謠」又係勁扣分</span></span></strong><br />\n大家都知咩叫造謠<br />\n佢話你造謠你就係造謠<br />\n評分系統扣你分連審道唔撚使<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">低分者有機會無得出境</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n一個監控評分系統<br />\n滿足佢三個願望<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">架空香港司法體制<br />\n廿三條直接回魂<br />\n出入境自由直接收皮</span></span></strong><br />\n基本法賦予嘅<br />\n司法獨立、言論自由、出入境自由<br />\n直接壽終正寢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">六大訴求缺一不可</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">拆除   監控燈柱<br />\n撤回    送中惡法<br />\n收回    暴動定義<br />\n撤銷    社運控罪<br />\n起訴    濫權黑警<br />\n落實    真雙普選<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"55c6e31e29385d7a0358afd8e0309cf4a131b789","tid":1430682,"uid":299171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T20:32:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">六大訴求缺一不可</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">拆除 監控燈柱<br />\n撤回 送中惡法<br />\n收回 暴動定義<br />\n撤銷 社運控罪<br />\n起訴 濫權黑警<br />\n落實 真雙普選</span>"},{"pid":"b81202861ff010e565f7c37fdf632258db28d089","tid":1430682,"uid":299171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T20:33:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>六大訴求缺一不可</strong></span><br />\n拆除 監控燈柱<br />\n撤回 送中惡法<br />\n收回 暴動定義<br />\n撤銷 社運控罪<br />\n起訴 濫權黑警<br />\n落實 真雙普選"},{"pid":"8d9bfd6e6d52159fe6caee322f5d23951eed2202","tid":1430682,"uid":232456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T20:36:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b78821876c6ad19f478457b4650d9dfc36634e3","tid":1430682,"uid":299171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:43:03.000Z","msg":"六大訴求缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n拆除 監控燈柱<br />\n撤回 送中惡法<br />\n收回 暴動定義<br />\n撤銷 社運控罪<br />\n起訴 濫權黑警<br />\n落實 真雙普選"},{"pid":"2da223930bc0d186854cf40ae74e2f3cc8e8b811","tid":1430682,"uid":299171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:43:16.000Z","msg":"六大訴求缺一不可<br />\n拆除 監控燈柱<br />\n撤回 送中惡法<br />\n收回 暴動定義<br />\n撤銷 社運控罪<br />\n起訴 濫權黑警<br />\n落實 真雙普選"},{"pid":"0681b57294f84aa8ef9a326c0b5d3ee1cfe8692e","tid":1430682,"uid":142007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:59:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2be297f001b2ec62dee76c782600d9c358eb879","tid":1430682,"uid":220368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:05:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9197e4dc785a60c48a758cec2f6242fca56c3984","tid":1430682,"uid":6674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:06:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c509b520b79c5993d72d039187b374491fd6a5c0","tid":1430682,"uid":7832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:15:02.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"6a7959d97ca913f3911cba00fa5f90eb443ffa33","tid":1430682,"uid":272087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T20:41:14.000Z","msg":"推。"}]}